title: No chest for S- or higher bug!?!
body: I just got ganked of a chest after getting an S on brand, yes i have chests available, i own him, i got no chat restrictions (if that even matters?), n i never got one with him yet he doesnt have the border of already completed so i legit got robbed...pretty frustrating after doin so well with a champ

replies.body: Its all good now, not sure why it wasnt showin up for you but i ended up gettin another S with him in the next game n got my chest this time :)

I'm not seeing any matches with Brand where you've gotten an S- or above. It might just be taking a bit for that match to fully upload if it just took place, but if it doesn't we'll need a screenshot of that S as some kind of proof so that we can double-check the system.
